  m_text: "These methods should be unlocked by the players. By using resources, the
    individual artefacts of the methods are unlocked and the methods are gradually
    developed.  \n\nIn the successive screen, players should invest resources in
    each of the methods which will have direct influence on the quality of the product.
    Hence the players should invest wisely in each methods based on the number of
    resources alloted. "
